Ian Gelder https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ian_Gelder 0 Ian Gelder (born 3 June 1949) is an English actor. He is known for his numerous stage and screen roles, including Mr Dekker in Torchwood: Children of Earth and Kevan Lannister in Game of Thrones. Ian_Gelder ( born 3_June_1949 ) is an_English_actor .
